  date: "2026-02-28"
  description: "TRINITY Orchestrator v2.0 - Universal command orchestration with sacred mathematics"

  features:
    - 137 commands registered (100% coverage)
    - 4 execution strategies (sequential, parallel, conditional, adaptive)
    - Sacred mathematics integration (φ-based scoring and decision making)
    - Thread-safe parallel execution
    - AST-based condition parsing
    - Adaptive workflow analysis

  readiness:
    code: COMPLETE
    tests: PASSING
    documentation: COMPLETE
    benchmarks: COMPLETE

